Brittany,

616
00:32:04,649 --> 00:32:06,747
vocę apoia a decisăo
do seu marido

617
00:32:06,748 --> 00:32:08,248
de encerrar a vida dele?

618
00:32:19,609 --> 00:32:21,009
Eu apoio.

619
00:32:23,471 --> 00:32:24,971
