<i>Voltem aqui.</i>

687
00:37:00,558 --> 00:37:02,951
<i>Lá vai, lá vai.</i>

688
00:37:06,681 --> 00:37:08,930
- O quę?
<i>- Elijah.</i>

689
00:37:09,977 --> 00:37:11,500
Dois a dois?

690
00:37:11,501 --> 00:37:13,372
Tigers
da Universidade de Memphis.

691
00:37:14,010 --> 00:37:15,914
<i>Estou do lado de quem?</i>

692
00:37:20,437 --> 00:37:21,837
Tręs a tręs!

693
00:37:21,838 --> 00:37:23,962
- Disse tręs em tręs?
